<article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" id="post-484877" class="post-484877 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-hackaday-columns category-linux-hacks category-slider tag-ghostscript tag-linux tag-pdf tag-postscript series_of_posts-linux-fu">
    <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name">Linux Fu: PDF For Penguins</h1>
        <div class="entry-meta">
            <a href="https://hackaday.com/2021/07/06/linux-fu-pdf-for-penguins/#comments" class="comments-counts"><span class="icon-hackaday icon-hackaday-comment"></span>
