			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Some other useful tools I use regularly:<br />
&#8211; pdfshuffler (for Debian/Ubuntu/Mint) or pdfslicer (for Arch Linux) to reorder or delete pages and mix documents)<br />
&#8211; krop to cut pdf to big to be printed on a single A4 page (useful for maps&#8230; just use some glue after :-)<br />
&#8211; pdfbook (alias to pdfjam) to save paper and made physical pretty booklets</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->
