			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I prefer EPUB over PDF, since EPUB flows to fit the display device geometry.  For conversion, I use Calibre to convert PDF to EPUB.  For editing, Sigil edits what looks like a HTML document, and outputs EPUB.  I kinda think Calibre lets you create PDFs and other formats from EPUB but I&#8217;ve not bothered.</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->
