			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>While we are talking about PDF&#8217;s, I sometimes use &#8216;pdfimages&#8217;, part of the poppler-utils package. It will extract all the images from a PDF file, saving them in jpg format.</p>
<p>pdfimages -all &#8220;mypdf.pdf&#8221; /media/Workspace/Temp/</p>
